Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xidha dusha sare ee unugyada wadnaha, wadnaha, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay la xiriirtaa waxqabadka enzymes angiotensin-converter (ACE) oo la xiriira yareynta tirada angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta Ang ((1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo la filayo in lagu bartilmaameedsado daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii xarun gelitaan unugyada loogu talagalay qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa zinc-ka ku jira metallosymmetry ee ku yaal dusha sare ee endothelium iyo unugyada kale.
Isticmaalka ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal colectin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiin nooc 1 ah oo ah habka loo yaqaan 'single-path' membrane protein, iyadoo domains-ka firfircoon ee enzyme-ka lagu muujiyo unugyada wadnaha iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 waxaa lagu dhejiyaa transmembrane by enzymes kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, waxaana lagu sii daayaa dhiigga, waxaana lagu qasi karaa kaadida.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha jirka badankood: ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xarkaha unugyada unugyada unugyada alveolus nooca II ee sanbabada, entrosites-ka mindhicirka yar, unugyada wadnaha iyo unugyada endothelium-ka iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee unugyada unugyada badankood.
Isticmaalka mRNA ee ACE2 waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, striatum, hypothalamus iyo maskaxda.
