ACE2 waxay ku dhejisaa phenylalanine amino acid carboxyl-terminal angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) iyo hydrolysis-keeda angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku dhejin kartaa dhowr peptides oo kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]- bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A iyo ghrelin.
