Dib-u-habeynta ACE2 (rhACE2) ee aadanaha waxaa loo tixgeliyaa inay tahay daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sanbabada ee degdegga ah, waxayna u muuqataa inay hagaajineyso hawo-dhaqaajinta sanbabada iyo oksijiinta oksijiinta ee doofaarka leh cudurka 'lipopolysaccharide-affected acute respiratory distress syndrome'.
Nolosha nuska ah ee rhACE2 ee bini'aadamka waa 10 saacadood, bilowga tallaabada waa 30 daqiiqo marka lagu daro tallaabada saameynta (waqtiga) ee 24-ka saac.
Qaar ka mid ah natiijooyinka ayaa soo jeedinaya in rhACE2 ay noqon karto dawo la filayo oo loogu talagalay kuwa aan u dulqaadan karin nidaamka caadiga ah ee angiotensin renin (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurada ku xeeran angiotensin II ee la xoojiyay. rhACE2 infusion ayaa lagu qiimeeyay daraasad caafimaad oo loogu talagalay daaweynta cudurka neefsashada oo aad u daran.
