Australia iyo New Zealand ayaa ka fiirsanaya codsiyada ku saleysan codsiga Singapore ee TraceTogether iyo BlueTrace protocol. Ruushka wuxuu damacsan yahay inuu soo bandhigo codsi geoborder ah bukaannada laga helay COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, oo loogu talagalay in lagu hubiyo inaysan guriga ka bixin.
